<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٥٢ ... سُورَةُ الطُّورِ ... آياتها ٤٩ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالطُّورِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالجَبَلِ الَّذِي كَلَّمَ اللهُ عَلَيْهِ مُوسَى - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَكِتَابٍ مَّسْطُورٍ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالقُرْآنِ المَكْتُوبِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِي رَقٍّ مَّنشُورٍ}</span> ... فَي صُحُفٍ مَنْشُورَةٍ، مَبْسُوطَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْبَيْتِ الْمَعْمُورِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالبَيْتِ المَعْمُورِ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ الَّذِينَ يَطُوفُونَ بِهِ دَائِمًا، وَهُوَ فيِ السَّمَاءِ بِحِذَاءِ الكَعْبَةِ، يَطُوفُ بِهِ كُلَّ يَوْمٍ سَبْعُونَ أَلْفَ مَلَكٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالسَّقْفِ الْمَرْفُوعِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالسَّمَاءِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَسْجُورِ}</span> ... المَمْلُوءِ بِالمَاءِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَمُورُ}</span> ... تَتَحَرَّكُ، وَتَضْطَرِبُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُدَعُّونَ}</span> ... يُدْفَعُونَ بِعُنْفٍ وَشِدَّةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اصْلَوْهَا}</span> ... ادْخُلُوهَا، وذُوقُوا حَرَّهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاكِهِينَ}</span> ... مُتَلَذِّذِينَ، نَاعِمِينَ، مَسْرُورِينَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّصْفُوفَةٍ}</span> ... مُتَقَابِلَةٍ، وَبَعْضُهَا إِلَى جَنْبِ بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِحُورٍ}</span> ... نِسَاءٍ بِيضٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عِينٍ}</span> ... وَاسِعَاتِ العُيُونِ، حِسَانِهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا أَلَتْنَاهُم}</span> ... مَا نَقَصْنَا الآبَاءَ بِهَذَا الإِلْحَاقِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>